            <description><![CDATA[【👋🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%B7%9F%E8%85%B0%E9%85%B8%E8%83%8C%E7%97%9B%E8%AF%B4%E6%8B%9C%E6%8B%9C%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%B7%9F%E8%85%B0%E9%85%B8%E8%83%8C%E7%97%9B%E8%AF%B4%E6%8B%9C%E6%8B%9C%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#跟腰酸背痛说拜拜#</span></a> 】搬了6天砖，全身僵硬，腰酸背痛了<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[摊手]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_tanshou-fa05d4eacf.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> 3个简单的动作，帮你缓解：①上举夹背；②外旋夹背；③划船夹背👇🏻在家练起来，下周好继续搬砖<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" data-rsshub-image="href" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（CCTV生活圈）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4982422672965671" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">CCTV生活圈的微博视频</span></a> <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/orj480/713e54f1gy1hl4oh01fi2j20u0140h93.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/9Y58fxCtlx08bbOgZfF601041200opgt0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=720x1276.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1708938933&amp;ssig=tTBX1LptE4&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/8k3WdUjMlx08bbOhE2Ao01041200f78H0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=540x956.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1708938933&amp;ssig=6QrEnVR1dR&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source s